reviews.review_text: Summer 89 Some great shows in July of 89. This Alpine Show is an excellent example. This is more party Dead than jam Dead but it makes for a fun sunny summer-day listen. Excellent and rare Sugar Begonias with a Sunshine Daydream closer. Great Eyes as well.
